content:
Associate multiple service contracts from different accounts to the same asset to make it easier to track the history of work performed for the asset. For example, associate a leased vehicle to the leasee and leaser accounts to manage a separate service contract for each. Previously, you could only connect an asset to a single account and contact.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
title: Linking Assets to Multiple Accounts and Contacts in Salesforce
